---
title: Maple Bacon-Wrapped Chicken with Loaded Potato Wedges
description: Buckle up because this restaurant-worthy feast is about to take your taste buds on a ride! Tender chicken is covered in smoky bacon and a sweet and salty mix of maple syrup and BBQ seasoning. Loaded potato wedges take this hearty dinner to the next level!
